`;

exports[`reflect.on.reviews.self (acceptance) given: [case3] a caller who asks for --help when: [t0] the skill is dispatched with --help then: the usage guide matches its snapshot 1`] = `
"🌲 reflect.on.reviews.self — diagnose which init.behavior self-reviews earn their keep

usage:
  rhx reflect.on.reviews.self [--mode plan|apply] [--route <dir>] [--project <slug>]
                          [--stone <name>] [--brain <choice>] [--into <path>]

options:
  --mode     plan (signals only) | apply (+ brain verdicts)  [default: plan]
  --route    filter to windows of one route dir              [default: all routes]
  --project  filter to one project slug                      [default: all projects]
  --stone    filter to one stone (e.g. 1.vision)             [default: all stones]
  --brain    cheap brain choice for apply mode               [default: fireworks/deepseek/v4-flash]
  --into     report output path                              [default: ~/.rhachet/reflect, or into --route dir]
  --help     show this guide

with no flags, the skill sweeps every transcript in every project on the machine.
plan mode needs no brain; apply mode judges each window with the cheap brain."
`;

